'''国民志愿服务团'''（[[英语|英语]]：{{lang|en|Rashtriya Swayamsevak Sangh}}，简称RSS）是印度[[極右翼|极右翼]]、{{Tsl|en|Hindu Nationalism|印度教民族主义|印度教民族主义}}、全男性的[[準軍事組織|准军事志愿者组织]]<ref name="Horowitz">{{cite book|last1=Horowitz|first1=Donald L.|title=The Deadly Ethnic Riot|year=2001|publisher=[[University_of_California_Press|University of California Press]]|isbn=978-0520224476|page=[https://archive.org/details/deadlyethnicriot00horo/page/244 244]|url=https://archive.org/details/deadlyethnicriot00horo/page/244}}</ref><ref name="Haynes2003">{{cite book|author=Jeff Haynes|title=Democracy and Political Change in the Third World|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YdWAAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA168|date=2003-09-02|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-134-54184-3|pages=168–|access-date=2016-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170423174835/https://books.google.com/books?id=YdWAAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA168|archive-date=2017-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="McLeod2002">{{cite book|last1=McLeod|first1=John|title=The history of India|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DAwmUphO6eAC&pg=PA209|accessdate=2010-06-11|year=2002|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|isbn=978-0-313-31459-9|pages=209–|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424015646/https://books.google.com/books?id=DAwmUphO6eAC&pg=PA209|archive-date=2017-04-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。国民志愿服务团有诸多外围组织，被称为 Sangh Parivar（“服务团家族”），團員遍及印度社会各階層。国民志愿服务团成立于1925年9月27日。截至2019年，它的会员人数至少有500万<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=The Powerful Group Shaping The Rise Of Hindu Nationalism In India|url=https://www.npr.org/2019/05/03/706808616/the-powerful-group-shaping-the-rise-of-hindu-nationalism-in-india|accessdate=2020-10-19|work=NPR.org|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120163425/https://www.npr.org/2019/05/03/706808616/the-powerful-group-shaping-the-rise-of-hindu-nationalism-in-india|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[印度人民党|印度人民党]]被广泛认为与国民意志服务团有深刻联系；印度总理[[纳伦德拉·莫迪|纳伦德拉·莫迪]]、印度总统和内阁中的大多数人都是服务团成员<ref name=":0" />。

国民志愿服务团最初的目标是通过印度教纪律来训练成员品格，并团结[[印度教|印度教]]社会形成一个印度教国家（Hindu Rashtra）。该组织提倡维护印度文化和公民社会的价值观、传播印度教思想、以强化印度教社会<ref name="Dina Nath Mishra">{{cite book|last=Dina Nath Mishra|title=RSS: Myth and Reality|year=1980|publisher=Vikas Publishing House|isbn=978-0706910209|page=24}}</ref><ref name="Jaffrelot 2010">{{cite book|last1=Jaffrelot|first1=Christophe|title=Religion, Caste, and Politics in India|date=2010|publisher=Primus Books|isbn=9789380607047|page=46|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XAO3i_gS61wC&pg=PA46|language=en|access-date=2020-10-19|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114000827/https://books.google.com/books?id=XAO3i_gS61wC&pg=PA46}}</ref>。它的灵感来自于二战期间的欧洲极右翼团体<ref name="Atkins2004">{{cite book|last1=Atkins|first1=Stephen E.|title=Encyclopedia of modern worldwide extremists and extremist groups|url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofmo0000atki|url-access=registration|accessdate=2010-05-26|year=2004|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|isbn=978-0-313-32485-7|pages=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofmo0000atki/page/264 264]–265}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Hindutva's Foreign Tie-Up in the 1930s: Archival Evidence|last=Casolari|first=Marzia|date=2000|journal=Economic and Political Weekly|issue=4|volume=35|pages=218–228|issn=0012-9976|jstor=4408848}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title='Physiological Patriots'?: The Politics of Physical Culture and Hindu Nationalism in India|last=McDonald|first=Ian|date=1999-12-01|journal=International Review for the Sociology of Sport|publisher=Sage Journals|issue=4|doi=10.1177/101269099034004003|volume=34|pages=343–358|language=en|issn=1012-6902|s2cid=144111156}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Searching for a Progressive Hindu/ism: Battling Mussolini's Hindus, Hindutva, and Hubris|url=https://muse.jhu.edu/article/595824/summary|last=Natrajan|first=Balmurli|date=2009|journal=Tikkun|publisher=Duke University Press|issue=5|doi=10.1215/08879982-2009-5024|volume=24|pages=58–61|language=en|issn=2164-0041|s2cid=171206784|via=}}</ref>。国民志愿服务团此后逐渐发展成为印度教民族主义伞式组织，催生了多个附属组织，建立了许多学校、慈善机构和社团来传播其思想信仰<ref name="Atkins2004" />。服务团不公布其年度预算，但表示所有资金都来自私人捐款<ref name=":0" />。成为会员是免费的，可以通过在线填写表格加入<ref name=":0" />。

在[[英属印度|英国统治印度]]期间，国民志愿服务团曾被取缔过一次，后又被[[印度|印度]]政府取缔过三次：第一次是在1948年，[[南度蓝姆·高德西|南度蓝姆·高德西]]暗杀[[圣雄甘地|甘地]]后（南度蓝姆·高德西称因分歧已离开服务团）<ref name=":2">—{{cite book|last1=Karawan|first1=Ibrahim A.|last2=McCormack|first2=Wayne|last3=Reynolds|first3=Stephen E.|title=Values and Violence: Intangible Aspects of Terrorism|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ol-63orWw68C&pg=PA87|year=2008|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-1-4020-8660-1|page=87|access-date=2020-10-19|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116175754/https://books.google.com/books?id=ol-63orWw68C&pg=PA87}}

—{{cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/nathuram-godse-never-left-rss-says-his-family/articleshow/54159375.cms|title=Nathuram Godse never left RSS, says his family|first1=Vasudha|last1=Venugopal|date=2016-09-08|newspaper=The Economic Times|accessdate=2020-10-19|archive-date=2017-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520234812/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/nathuram-godse-never-left-rss-says-his-family/articleshow/54159375.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Atkins2004" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2004/08/18/stories/2004081805151100.htm|title=RSS releases 'proof' of its innocence|newspaper=The Hindu|date=2004-08-18|accessdate=2011-01-26|location=Chennai, India|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040905230837/http://www.hindu.com/2004/08/18/stories/2004081805151100.htm|archive-date=2004-09-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="IAR">{{cite book|author=Gerald James Larson|title=India's Agony Over Religion|url=https://archive.org/details/indiasagonyoverr0000lars|publisher=[[State_University_of_New_York_Press|State University of New York Press]]|year=1995|page=[https://archive.org/details/indiasagonyoverr0000lars/page/132 132]|isbn=0-7914-2412-X}}</ref>；第二次是在[[紧急状态_(印度)|印度紧急状态]]期间（1975－1977年）；第三次是在1992年{{Tsl|en|Babri Masjid|巴布里清真寺|巴布里清真寺}}被拆除后。

== 历史 ==

=== 英属印度时期 ===
国民志愿服务团创立于 1925 年，创立者为医生{{Tsl|en|Keshav Baliram Hedgewar|4=Keshav Baliram Hedgewar}}<ref name=":0" />。组织的使命包括追求印度独立，及回应印度教及穆斯林之间的暴乱<ref name=":0" />。与宣扬非暴力的[[圣雄甘地|甘地]]不同，国民志愿服务团则强调军事纪律和印度教经文<ref name=":0" />。

Hedgewar 曾批评[[印度国民大会党|印度国大党]]领导层的宗教多元性<ref name=":0" />，也不愿团结穆斯林以抗争英国人{{sfn|Nussbaum, The Clash Within|2008|p=156}}{{sfn|Bhatt, Hindu Nationalism|2001|p=115}}。服务团的早期领袖 {{Tsl|en|M. S. Golwalkar|4=M. S. Golwalkar}} 曾将基督徒和穆斯林称为印度的“内部威胁”，并称印度可以学习纳粹德国的“种族自豪感”。但服务团领导人支持建立以色列作为犹太人的国家<ref>{{cite report|url=http://www.nhsf.org.uk/images/stories/HinduDharma/Interfaith/hinduzion.pdf|title=Hindu Pro-Zionism and Philo-Semitism|last1=Quraiza|first1=Jai Banu|date=January 2004|page=84|access-date=11 April 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060423090103/http://www.nhsf.org.uk/images/stories/HinduDharma/Interfaith/hinduzion.pdf|url-status=dead|archivedate=2006-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Golwalkar钦佩犹太人保持其“宗教、文化和语言”<ref>{{cite book|title=Golwalkar's We or our nationhood defined: a critique|page=30|publisher=Pharos Media & Pub.|year=2006|author=Shamsul Islam}}</ref>。2006年，国民志愿服务团试图与 Golwalkar 的著作《We or Our Nationhood Defined》保持距离，称该组织不再同意其中的一些观点<ref>{{Cite web|title=RSS officially disowns Golwalkar's book {{!}} India News - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/RSS-officially-disowns-Golwalkars-book/articleshow/1443606.cms|accessdate=2020-10-19|last=Mar 9|first=Akshaya Mukul / TNN /|work=The Times of India|language=en|archive-date=2018-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180106073144/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/RSS-officially-disowns-Golwalkars-book/articleshow/1443606.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

虽然国民志愿服务团追求印度独立，但在 Hedgewar 的领导下并没有组织实质性运动，也没有与当时反抗英国统治的组织有直接联系{{sfn|Shamsul Islam, Religious Dimensions|2006|p=188}}。服务团没有支持国大党的 1930 年[[印度独立宣言|印度独立宣言]]或者代表印度独立的[[印度国旗|三色旗]]<ref name="Hadiz2006">{{cite book|author=Vedi R. Hadiz|title=Empire and Neoliberalism in Asia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dd99AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA252|date=27 September 2006|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-134-16727-2|pages=252–|access-date=13 February 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118113508/https://books.google.com/books?id=dd99AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA252|archive-date=2017-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其后，在Golwalkar的领导下，服务团也与独立运动保持了距离。Golwalkar认为服务团承诺通过“捍卫宗教和文化”来实现自由，而不是通过与英国人抗争<ref name="Golwalkar1974">{{cite book|author=M. S. Golwalkar|title=Shri Guruji Samgra Darshan, Volume 4|date=1974|publisher=Bharatiya Vichar Sadhana}}</ref>{{sfn|Shamsul Islam, Religious Dimensions|2006|p=191}}{{sfn|Puniyani, Religion, Power and Violence|2005|p=135}}。Golwalkar 不想给英国人借口来取缔服务团。他遵守了英属印度政府在[[第二次世界大战|二战]]期间实施的所有限制措施，甚至宣布终止服务团的军事化组织{{sfn|Andersen|Damle|1987}}{{sfn|Noorani, RSS and the BJP|2000|p=46}}。国民志愿务团没有参加[[退出印度运动|退出印度运动{{sfn]][[国民志愿服务团#cite%20note-FOOTNOTEShamsul%20Islam%2C%20Religious%20Dimensions2006187-24|<span class="mw-reflink-text">[24]</span>]]或者 1946 年的[[皇家印度海军兵变|皇家印度海军兵变{{sfn]][[国民志愿服务团#cite%20note-FOOTNOTEBhatt%2C%20Hindu%20Nationalism2001115-15|<span class="mw-reflink-text">[15]</span>]]。英属印度政府也未认为服务团对印度治安有过威胁{{sfn|Bipan Chandra, Communalism|2008|p=140}}{{sfn|Andersen|Damle|1987}}{{sfn|Noorani, RSS and the BJP|2000|p=46}}。Golwalkar 承认服务团未积极参与独立运动，以至民意认为服务团空有声明，但在现实中没有意义<ref name="Golwalkar19742">{{cite book|author=M. S. Golwalkar|title=Shri Guruji Samgra Darshan, Volume 4|date=1974|publisher=Bharatiya Vichar Sadhana}}</ref>{{sfn|Shamsul Islam, Religious Dimensions|2006|p=187}}。

=== 印度独立后 ===
[[File:Rashtriya_Swayamsewak_Sangh_drill.jpg|thumb]]
1948 年，印度独立不久，[[南度蓝姆·高德西|南度蓝姆·高德西]]便因不满[[圣雄甘地|圣雄甘地]]试图弥合印度教徒及穆斯林的目标，将甘地射杀<ref name=":0" />。国民志愿服务团承认高德西曾是该组织成员，但认为他是极端分子，在甘地被杀时已经离开组织<ref name=":0" />。亦有其他人，包括高德西的亲属，认为他从未离开服务团 <ref>{{Cite news|title=Nathuram Godse never left RSS, says his family|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/nathuram-godse-never-left-rss-says-his-family/articleshow/54159375.cms|newspaper=The Economic Times|accessdate=2020-10-19|first=Vasudha|last=Venugopal|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116175727/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/nathuram-godse-never-left-rss-says-his-family/articleshow/54159375.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。官方的调查认为国民志愿服务团对甘地之死不付责任<ref name=":0" />。

1975年，[[英迪拉·甘地|英迪拉·甘地]]政府宣布印度实行[[紧急状态_(印度)|紧急状态]]，并冻结基本权利、限制新闻自由<ref name="emma">Emma Tarlo, ''Unsettling Memories: Narratives of India's "emergency"'', Published by Orient Blackswan, 2003, {{ISBN|81-7824-066-1}}, {{ISBN|978-81-7824-066-4}}</ref>。此前，[[印度最高法院|印度最高法院]]以选举舞弊为由，取消了甘地在印度议会的席位<ref name="emma2">Emma Tarlo, ''Unsettling Memories: Narratives of India's "emergency"'', Published by Orient Blackswan, 2003, {{ISBN|81-7824-066-1}}, {{ISBN|978-81-7824-066-4}}</ref>。国民志愿服务团被认为与反对派领导人关系密切、组织基础庞大、有能力组织反对政府的抗议活动，也因此被禁止{{sfn|Jaffrelot, Hindu Nationalism Reader|2007|p=297}}。

时任服务团领袖 Deoras 曾致信英迪拉·甘地，承诺与她合作，以换取解禁，并曾试图寻找中间人与政府进行调解{{sfn|Tapan Basu, Khaki Shorts|1993|pp=51–54}}{{sfn|Noorani, RSS and the BJP|2000|p=31}}。因政府没有回应，服务团开始了反对紧急状态的地下运动，直至紧急状态解除<ref>Post Independence India, Encyclopedia of Political Parties, 2002, published by Anmol Publications PVT. LTD, {{ISBN|81-7488-865-9}}, {{ISBN|978-81-7488-865-5}}</ref><ref>page 238, Encyclopedia of Political parties, Volumes 33–50 https://books.google.com/books?id=QCh_yd357iIC&pg=PA238</ref>。有学者认为服务团在紧急状态时期的作用强化了其在印度政治中合法性，从而为随后的印度教政治播下了种子<ref name=":03">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YwvaaHI8sjEC&pg=PA110|title=The Politics of Personal Law in South Asia: Identity, Nationalism and the Uniform Civil Code|last1=Ghosh|first1=Partha S.|date=23 May 2012|publisher=Routledge|isbn=9781136705113|pages=110–112|language=en|access-date=2020-10-21|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114000831/https://books.google.com/books?id=YwvaaHI8sjEC&pg=PA110}}</ref>。此前，1948年的甘地暗杀案一直是服务团的污点<ref name=":03" />。

1980年代，国民志愿服务团因呼吁在印度北部城市[[阿约提亚|阿约提亚]]建造印度教寺庙而知名。阿约提亚被认为是印度教神祇[[羅摩|罗摩]]的出生地，但罗摩的出生地点已有一座16世纪建造的{{Tsl|en|Babri Masjid|巴布里清真寺|巴布里清真寺}}<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|title=印度最高法院判决“世界最具争议”房地产案|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-50360524|newspaper=BBC News 中文|accessdate=2020-10-19|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116175757/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-50360524|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1992年，印度教信众摧毁了该清真寺。之后，近两千人在骚乱中死亡，其中大部分是穆斯林<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />。截止 2020 年，[[罗摩神庙|罗摩神庙]]已经开始兴建<ref name=":1" />。

== 目标 ==
[[印度宪法|印度宪法]]将其定义为[[世俗國家|世俗国家]]，但国民志愿服务团的使命声明称其“坚定地植根于真正的民族主义”，并谴责“以世俗主义的名义侵蚀国家的完整性”和“无休止地姑息穆斯林人口”<ref name=":0" />。

